#set($subject = "Welcome to RidesIQ - Set Up Your Account")

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to RidesIQ</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafc;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #7ca6ff, #7ee6c6);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      background-color: #7ca6ff;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .info-table {
      margin: 30px auto 0 auto;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .info-table td {
      padding: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .info-table td.label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #555;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .info-table td.value {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 12px;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .warning-box strong {
      color: #856404;
    }
    .totp-section {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .totp-section h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .totp-qr {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .totp-qr img {
      max-width: 200px;
      border: 2px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: white;
    }
    .totp-secret {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      word-break: break-all;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }
    .steps {
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .steps li {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
    }
    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="title">Welcome to RidesIQ!</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi $user.name,</p>
      <p>Your RidesIQ account has been created successfully. To get started, you need to set up your password and two-factor authentication.</p>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Steps:</strong>
        <ol style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <li>Click the button below to set your password</li>
          <li>Set up two-factor authentication using the QR code provided below</li>
          <li>This link will expire in 24 hours for your security</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="label">Email:</td>
          <td class="value">$user.email</td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <a href="$webUrl/reset-password?passwordReset=$token" class="cta-button">Set Your Password</a>

      <div class="totp-section">
        <h3>üîê Two-Factor Authentication Setup</h3>
        <p>For enhanced security, two-factor authentication (2FA) has been enabled on your account. Follow these steps to complete the setup:</p>
        
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Download an authenticator app (Google Authenticator, Authy, Microsoft Authenticator, etc.)</li>
          <li>Open the app and scan the QR code below, or manually enter the secret key</li>
          <li>The app will generate a 6-digit code that changes every 30 seconds</li>
          <li>Use this code along with your password when logging in</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="totp-qr">
          <img src="$totpQrCodeUrl" alt="TOTP QR Code" />
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0;"><strong>Or manually enter this secret key:</strong></p>
        <div class="totp-secret">$user.totpKey</div>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">After setting your password and configuring 2FA, you can log in to your account.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Stay safe, <br/><strong>The RidesIQ Team</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2025 RidesIQ. All rights reserved. | <a href="https://www.ridesiq.com/privacy-policy" style="color: #999; text-decoration: underline;">Privacy Policy</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
